The faux-suede lining is bonded to ensure both durability and a lightweight feel.

description: Cast-iron bottle opener modeled after the authentic Double RL Ranch brand. Naturally corroded for a vintage look. "Double RL" debossed at the handle.

name: intrecciato weave zip-around wallet
description: Brown calf leather intrecciato weave zip-around wallet from Bottega Veneta featuring an all around zip fastening, an interior zipped compartment, multiple interior card slots, internal slip pockets and an embossed internal logo stamp.

name: Ralph Lauren Medium Leather Crossbody Bag in Lauren Tan - Size One Size
description: Crafted from pebbled leather and finished with a polished "LRL" logo closure this crossbody bag will hold your essentials in style.

name: Ralph Lauren Leather Medium Bellport Tote in Saddle - Size One Size
description: Crafted from American full-grain calfskin that's tanned and finished in Italy the Bellport tote is bonded to sumptuous suede at the interior making it fully reversible while maintaining its effortless structure. Designed with versatility in mind this spacious bag delivers two looks in one: a classic tote silhouette and a trapezoid-shaped silhouette which is achieved by looping the leather strap at the top right through the D-ring at the top left.

name: Ralph Lauren Heritage Leather Folio in Brown - Size One Size
description: This handsome full-grain leather folio holds paperwork notebooks and documents in style. The Polo Heritage logo lends a distinctive touch.

name: zip around wallet
description: Founded in 1913 by Mario Prada, the brand is renowned for their timeless designs with traditional Milanese craftsmanship at its helm. Expect to see outerwear with a utilitarian twist and luxurious accessories that have amassed a cult following. This classic continental wallet has been crafted from the label鈥檚 iconic Peonia Pink Saffiano leather, featuring a zip fastening, multiple interior card slots, a zipped coin pouch, note compartments and a Prada logo plaque at the centre.

name: Ralph Lauren Calfskin Mini RL50 Handbag in RL Gold - Size One Size
description: Drawing inspiration from one of Mr. Lauren's personal travel bags The RL50 Handbag is defined by its belted silhouette and elegantly curved bar topline. Rendered in smooth calfskin and distinguished by polished hardware this mini version encapsulates Ralph Lauren's commitment to preserving artisanal leatherworking traditions as it's entirely handcrafted in a family-owned Italian studio. Completed with "RL"-engraved protective feet at the base our newest icon was conceived in the year of Ralph Lauren's 50th anniversary but updated this season in one of the Pre-Spring 2020 Collection's signature hues.

name: Ralph Lauren Clear Medium Tote in Clear/Vanilla - Size One Size
description: Perfect for carrying your everyday needs this tote bag is designed with a transparent body and a removable zip pouch.

name: Ralph Lauren Mini Debby II Drawstring Bag in Ruby/Nude - Size One Size
